Towie’s Chloe Lewis opened up about her devastating heartbreak after learning she was expecting twins while going through a miscarriage. The 28-year-old star, who is due to give birth to her baby in the next few weeks, only found out she was carrying twins when she began bleeding in her first trimester, she revealed to OK! Magazine. Lewis woke up one night to find bleeding and fearing the worst, she rushed to hospital where they told her she had been carrying two babies. Speaking to the magazine, she said: “I told her about the bleeding and she said that I probably had lost it